    "body": "This is a consequence of our cli library upgrade. In your command-line invocation, the flag `--exec` comes after the argument `/root/eth-node/datadir/geth.ipc`. With geth v1.10.20, this is no longer allowed by the cli parser, and you need to give the flag before the argument instead:\r\n\r\n```\r\n./geth_ethereum attach --exec \"admin.nodeInfo\" /root/eth-node/datadir/geth.ipc\r\n```\r\n\r\nI added an error in other commands like `account import` for this case, but didn't add it in `attach`.",
